Roll out. Roll over. Come on, man.

265
00:20:35,850 --> 00:20:37,485
Come on, Jerry, let's go!

266
00:20:38,185 --> 00:20:40,387
Alright, just go out.

267
00:20:40,487 --> 00:20:42,916
Son of a bitch, you are lucky!

268
00:20:46,461 --> 00:20:49,130
