Home-boy here plowed straight into me.

331
00:24:49,069 --> 00:24:51,238
Wait a second.
That doesn't add up at all.

332
00:24:51,338 --> 00:24:54,191
- No shit!
- <i>Radio for 2670.</i>

333
00:24:54,291 --> 00:24:57,445
- Go for 670.
