what they do to cop-killers in prison?

387
00:29:35,555 --> 00:29:39,226
<i>For me to go to prison
I would have to get caught first.</i>

388
00:29:39,326 --> 00:29:41,362
<i>But I have no intention
of getting caught.</i>

389
00:29:41,462 --> 00:29:45,266
