00:33:07,067 --> 00:33:08,812
No.

436
00:33:08,912 --> 00:33:11,071
<i>2670.</i>

437
00:33:11,171 --> 00:33:12,776
Go, 670.

438
00:33:12,876 --> 00:33:16,176
<i>I've got a report of a signal 42
